item.title: Nadigadda Rights Struggle Committee Backs “Jagriti Janam Bata” Program in Jogulamba Gadwal District
item.description:
<![CDATA[Gadwal: The Nadigadda Rights Struggle Committee has extended its support to the “Jagriti Janam Bata” program being organized by Telangana Jagriti President and MLC Kalvakuntla Kavitha during her visit to Jogulamba Gadwal district on the 21st and 22nd of this month.
As part of the preparations, the “Jagriti Janam Bata” wall poster was formally unveiled at the district office of the Nadigadda Rights Struggle Committee by NHPS District Chairman Gongalla Ranjith Kumar, along with committee leaders....]]>
item.author: M Veeresh, Big Story, Tech News
